'''''Soleil Ô''''' ( [sɔ.lɛj o] ; "Oh, Sun") ni filime yikinamico yo  mu gifaransa-Mauritanian yanditswe kandi iyobowe na Med Hondo<ref>Soleil O Oh Sun | The New Yorker <nowiki>https://www.newyorker.com</nowiki> › movies › soleil-o-oh-sun</ref> .

== Umugambi ==
Filime ''Soleil'' , yakozwe mu myaka ine n’ingengo y’imari iciriritse cyane, ivuga amateka y’umwimukira w'umwirabura winjiye i Paris ashakisha “abakurambere be ba Gaul”<ref>Soleil Ô - La Cinémathèque québécoise <nowiki>https://www.cinematheque.qc.ca</nowiki> › cinema › soleil-o</ref>. Iyi manifeste ya firime iramagana ivangura: Abimukira bashaka cyane akazi n’aho baba<ref>Soleil Ô (2017 restoration, The Film Foundation's World ... <nowiki>https://anttialanenfilmdiary.blogspot.com</nowiki> › 2017/06 › s...</ref>, ariko ugasanga imbonankubone batitaweho, bakangwa, kandi bagasuzugurwa, mbere yo kumvira umuhamagaro wa nyuma wo kwigomeka<ref>Soleil Ô (1967) Movie. Where To Watch Streaming Online <nowiki>https://moviefit.me</nowiki> › titles › 128232-soleil-o</ref>.

Umutwe werekeza ku ndirimbo yo mu Burengerazuba bw'Ubuhinde ivuga ububabare bw'abirabura bo muri Dahomey (ubu ni [[Bene|Bénin]] ) bajyanywe muri Karayibe nk'abacakara.

